        <updateDate>2020-04-27T15:03:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>VA-DoD Shared Medical Facilities Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Defense and the Department of Veterans Affairs to enter into agreements for the planning, design, and construction, or leasing, of facilities to be operated as shared medical facilities.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
